THIS BOOK CONTAINS PAPERS presented at the International Conference on Application Specific Array Processors (ASAPâ€™95) at the Universite Louis Pasteur in Strasbourg, France on July 24 through 26, 1995. This is the ninth in a series of conferences, which started with the International Workshop on Systolic Arrays in Oxford, England in 1986, continued with the International Conferences on Systolic Arrays in San Diego, USA in 1988, and Killamey, Ireland in 1989, and evolved into the International Conferences on Application-Specific Array Processors in Princeton, New Jersey in 1990, Barcelona, Spain in 1991, Berkeley, California in 1992, Venice, Italy in 1993, and San Francisco, California in 1994.